    "body" : "<p>You can use <code>map</code> :</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; names = \n    personList.stream()\n              .map(Person::getName)\n              .collect(Collectors.toList());\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>EDIT :</p>\n\n<p>In order to combine the Lists of friend names, you need to use <code>flatMap</code> :</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; friendNames = \n    personList.stream()\n              .flatMap(e-&gt;e.getFriends().stream())\n              .collect(Collectors.toList());\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
